      • filterToResolution

        public void filterToResolution(double visibleResolution)
        Filters the distribution to remove peaks which are unlikely to an effect on how the distribution is rendered at a given resolution, i.e. to save rendering time by omitting clusters of smaller peaks which are very close to larger peaks
        Parameters:
        visibleResolution - The resolvable resolution below which clusters can be merged
